metadata.name: "Flectere si nequeo superos, Acheronta movebo"
metadata.description:
The truly initiated 
Hate war, 
And those that create it.

The ones who know death 
Respect and admire it, 
With every breath.

Emancipation of ignorance  
Is commerce for awareness.

"If Moral equality is an obstacle to human excellence, then so much the worse for moral equality" 

Flectere si nequeo superos, Acheronta movebo
